{"tid":1364380,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"明明放暑假 小妹妹點解唔去玩","createTime":"2019-07-25T10:46:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T15:27:49.000Z","uid":94499,"like":38,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"8d81ef9c6a1bf7a0109eb3ee681881ab9ce50ef8","tid":1364380,"uid":94499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T10:46:56.000Z","msg":"今日搭車經過見到呢到呢一幕，<br />\n大熱天時 一個小妹妹企係到痴返實每一張memo，<br />\n真係好心痛 係我地呢班哥哥姐姐對你唔住，<br />\n要你出嚟受呢啲苦，剝奪咗你快樂既童年，<br />\n明明放暑假，<br />\n你應該好開心去玩，留屋企嘆冷氣睇卡通片⋯<br />\n<br />\n我地下一代都比個班仆街更加知道要守護呢個家，<br />\n真係好想問佢地 到底有無羞恥之心，<br />\n佢地就有錢有能力 送班仔女去外國讀書 居留，<br />\n攪亂香港之後，就留底我地下一代執你地爛攤子，<br />\n正仆街，絕對唔可以俾林鄭拍個囉柚就走咗去，<br />\n一定要班高官，黑警，黑社會，何君堯 撐送中既議員 ⋯<br />\n十倍奉還！！！！<br />\n追究到底 還返我地下一代一個美好香港！ ！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xJfFJwP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxJfFJwP.png&h=c72936cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n若是問我可否將所想的封鎖<br />\n<br />\n就像問我絲巾可否包一堆火"},{"pid":"1ded17c74a64aed9ca54a0e9499bce341328bf62","tid":1364380,"uid":157282,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T10:50:08.000Z","msg":"哥哥姐姐們唔好再道歉啦！<br />\n無論幾多歲，第幾代，<br />\n關心社會都係一個公民嘅責任！<br />\n我地一齊繼續努力！"},{"pid":"e41a92cfcad4c438e6c70fd3fd3eb635da128ae8","tid":1364380,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T10:50:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a09ea250d5356932782e6a9259c912e19b6f880","tid":1364380,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T11:11:01.000Z","msg":"葵盛？"},{"pid":"e2b3f112451e1667784e74b81f43e4685a67c08f","tid":1364380,"uid":94499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a09ea250d5356932782e6a9259c912e19b6f880","tid":1364380,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T11:11:01.000Z","msg":"葵盛？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T11:27:32.000Z","msg":"係啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"004a73286a6a85013ca6496e801fe79bb11a7485","tid":1364380,"uid":36494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:06:22.000Z","msg":"平時見葵盛好多老人<br />\n一係就係啲甩皮甩骨新移民<br />\n無諗過個連儂牆可以搞得成<br />\n仲要暫時都未見有比人破壞"},{"pid":"92bc87679a1587c56d261cc1f135f9b903489ca3","tid":1364380,"uid":5178,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:07:03.000Z","msg":"加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c4a1a4230615a8e615381432a6e42f77b29eda5","tid":1364380,"uid":92908,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:08:42.000Z","msg":"催淚彈"},{"pid":"baf84abe9e05ced1f6e57152c7f2a1950d84ba70","tid":1364380,"uid":27991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:09:09.000Z","msg":"真係唔想過幾年後，見到 10 後出來抗爭 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bcb2ada1d18f0e3bd9f9a7865170ceae7f1fe29","tid":1364380,"uid":260325,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:09:19.000Z","msg":"27/7 元朗見"},{"pid":"e117803241761d1adfdb7b947d6c707adf2bd4fa","tid":1364380,"uid":182984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:09:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5855e1c94298194b439b0f2921e0be98d2a42a36","tid":1364380,"uid":77740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:15:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a8534cc636ce1327272f0c2dea9741344e11586","tid":1364380,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"baf84abe9e0